			<div class="wnd-body">
				<div class="wnd-body-inner"  style="">

The intent of this privacy policy is to detail: 
<div style="padding-left: 15px;">
	<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce.png?v=11829" height="5" alt="" width="5" class="png32" />&nbsp;The information that Magelo may gather about individuals who visit our websites and create accounts with us<br>
	<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce.png?v=11829" height="5" alt="" width="5" class="png32" />&nbsp;How that information is used<br>
	<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce.png?v=11829" height="5" alt="" width="5" class="png32" />&nbsp;Magelo's disclosure practices<br>
</div>
<br><br>

<div class="WINDOW-BODY-TITLE"><img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce_orange.png?v=11829" height="12" alt="" width="12" class="png32" />&nbsp;Site usage information</div>
<br>
Magelo gathers site usage information from all visitors to our websites. This data is used in the aggregate to help determine general usage patterns and to fine-tune layout so that our sites are as useful and enjoyable as possible. This site usage information does not contain any information which would identify an individual user. Generally it contains information such as (but not limited to):<br>
<br>
<div style="padding-left: 15px;">
	<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce.png?v=11829" height="5" alt="" width="5" class="png32" />&nbsp;What pages have been visited<br>
	<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce.png?v=11829" height="5" alt="" width="5" class="png32" />&nbsp;What pages referred visitors to our sites<br>
	<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce.png?v=11829" height="5" alt="" width="5" class="png32" />&nbsp;What search engine was used to find our sites<br>
	<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce.png?v=11829" height="5" alt="" width="5" class="png32" />&nbsp;What browsers and screen resolutions are used to view our websites<br>
	<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce.png?v=11829" height="5" alt="" width="5" class="png32" />&nbsp;What country visitors to our site are from<br>
	<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce.png?v=11829" height="5" alt="" width="5" class="png32" />&nbsp;How long a visitor remains on our website<br>
</div>

<br>
This site usage information and statistical data may be made public at Magelo's discretion.
<br><br>

<div class="WINDOW-BODY-TITLE"><img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce_orange.png?v=11829" height="12" alt="" width="12" class="png32" />&nbsp;Individual user information</div>
<br>
Individually identifiable information will not be released without that individual's prior consent. Visitors are specifically asked for individually identifiable information when signing up for certain Magelo services. All information which would be individually identifiable (including billing information) is only transmitted over a Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) framework which encrypts information for your protection. From time to time, Magelo may contact individual users who have provided information to us for reasons such as (but is not limited to):
<br><br>
<div style="padding-left: 15px;">
	<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce.png?v=11829" height="5" alt="" width="5" class="png32" />&nbsp;Receipts for transactions<br>
	<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce.png?v=11829" height="5" alt="" width="5" class="png32" />&nbsp;Password reminders<br>
	<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce.png?v=11829" height="5" alt="" width="5" class="png32" />&nbsp;Support<br>  
</div>

<br><br>
<div class="WINDOW-BODY-TITLE"><img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce_orange.png?v=11829" height="12" alt="" width="12" class="png32" />&nbsp;Credit card security</div>
<br>
We collect credit card information for the purpose of conducting financial transactions with account holders. These transactions are conducted using Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) software, which encrypts the information both sent and received. We do not store any credit card information on our servers. 
<br><br>

<div class="WINDOW-BODY-TITLE"><img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/picto/home_puce_orange.png?v=11829" height="12" alt="" width="12" class="png32" />&nbsp;Credit card statement</div>
<br>
Should you conduct a credit card transaction with us, "Magelo" will appear on your credit card statement. 

<div align=center style="font-style: italic; font-size: 11px;">
	<br>
	Magelo does not sell, rent, lease or allow any third parties to view or use the information collected.<br>
	Magelo takes reasonable measures to keep the information disclosed secure.<br>
	However, Magelo assumes no responsibility for any breach of security to this data. 
</div>

